l polarization. If\nsignificant signal is detected in the U_phi images, we recommend to check the\nstandard Q and U images to look for departures from azimuthal polarization. On\nthe positive side, signal in the U_phi images once all instrumental and\ndata-reduction artifacts have been corrected for means that there is more\ninformation to be extracted regarding the dust population and particle density.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 22 Sep 2015 20:07:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-10-14"}
