ome\nprevious studies, we also show that 3C28 is an FR-II (rather than FR-I) source,\nand suggest that it is most likely a relic system with the central engine being\nturned off between 6 and 9 Myrs ago.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 22 Sep 2015 20:24:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-10-27"}
